by your brilliance?

1664
01:38:47,889 --> 01:38:50,258
Must we go through
this every time?

1665
01:38:50,325 --> 01:38:52,860
Come here. Come here.

1666
01:39:09,644 --> 01:39:11,779
Good. That's very good.

1667
01:39:11,846 --> 01:39:13,215
