1676
01:39:40,008 --> 01:39:41,176
except he's having
a heart attack.

1677
01:39:43,145 --> 01:39:44,979
And she's, like,
totally creeped out

1678
01:39:45,047 --> 01:39:48,116
and her mom, who basically
despises the guy,

1679
01:39:48,183 --> 01:39:50,952
