and saves his life.

1680
01:39:51,719 --> 01:39:53,755
Are you okay?

1681
01:39:53,821 --> 01:39:55,257
Isn't that funny?

1682
01:39:55,323 --> 01:39:58,560
Hold on, hold on.
Let's not get so dramatic here.

1683
01:39:58,626 --> 01:40:00,595
